explanations.reason: The paper focuses on the return sensitivity and volatility of public farmland and timberland REITs in relation to various asset classes, using a multi-factor asset pricing model and a state-space model with the Kalman filter. There is no mention or application of machine learning techniques, neural networks, or any of the other specified keywords in the title or abstract. The study is grounded in financial analysis and econometrics rather than machine learning or artificial intelligence.
